      • reformatDiagnostics

        public static String reformatDiagnostics(String orig)
        YARN diagnostics are verbose: they contain a stack trace of the YARN node manager thread (not Drill), and contain blank lines, the container ID, etc. Remove unnecessary cruft to make the diagnostics simpler and smaller in the Web UI.
        Parameters:
        orig - YARN diagnostics
        Returns:
        cleaned-up version.
